==== ENTRY 5 ====
HEADWORD: Tine
<hw>Tine</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>tind</ets>, AS.
<ets>tind</ets>; akin to MHG. <ets>zint</ets>, Icel. <ets>tindr</ets>,
Sw. <ets>tinne</ets>, and probably to G. <ets>zinne</ets> a pinnacle,
OHG. <ets>zinna</ets>, and E. <ets>tooth</ets>. See
<er>Tooth</er>.]</ety> <def>A tooth, or spike, as of a fork; a prong, as
of an antler.</def>⟦br⟧
